{
  "query": "query SyncBlogOwners($nextToken: String) {
  syncBlogOwners(nextToken: $nextToken) {
    items {
      _deleted
      _lastChangedAt
      _version
      blog {
        id
      }
      id
      name
      wea
    }
    nextToken
    startedAt
  }
}
",
  "variables": {
    "nextToken": ""
  }
}
